				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1  et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>List of Electives</h2></div>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
			</div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_2 et_pb_equal_columns">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_3 et_pb_column_2  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_0 et_animated  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light" data-animation-style="zoom" data-animation-repeat="" data-animation-duration="1000ms" data-animation-delay="0ms" data-animation-intensity="10%" data-animation-starting-opacity="0%" data-animation-speed-curve="ease-in-out">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Art</span></h4>
						<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Einstein Academy arts program has a well-rounded approach that addresses the needs of the whole child. Students in Pre-Kindergarten through High School participate in carefully designed lessons that challenge students to explore the world of art around them. Students manipulate materials to produce thought provoking and insightful products. Students also study art history, cultural arts, interdisciplinary projects and creative studio techniques. The Einstein Academy understands and values the arts and therefore fosters creativity with a rigorous arts program set up for success at any artistic level.</span></p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_3  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_1 et_animated  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light" data-animation-style="zoom" data-animation-repeat="" data-animation-duration="1000ms" data-animation-delay="0ms" data-animation-intensity="10%" data-animation-starting-opacity="0%" data-animation-speed-curve="ease-in-out">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Chorus (grades 6-12)</span></h4>
						<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Students work together to create a unified sound. Solfege singing techniques are emphasized. Students begin to explore harmonization and use their skills in performances, both informal and formal. </span></p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
			</div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_3">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_4  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_2 et_animated  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light" data-animation-style="zoom" data-animation-repeat="" data-animation-duration="1000ms" data-animation-delay="0ms" data-animation-intensity="10%" data-animation-starting-opacity="0%" data-animation-speed-curve="ease-in-out">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Drama &amp; Performance</span></h4>
						<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">All students grade PreK through high school will develop an appreciation of performance and the performing arts. Students will be exposed to various genres. Students will explore the history of dramatic interpretation and the creation of theatrical productions. Students will study theories, dramatic interpretations, character development, staging, scenery and tech work for lighting and sound.</span></p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_5  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_3 et_animated  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light" data-animation-style="zoom" data-animation-repeat="" data-animation-duration="1000ms" data-animation-delay="0ms" data-animation-intensity="10%" data-animation-starting-opacity="0%" data-animation-speed-curve="ease-in-out">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					
